    An abstract delegating implementation of Injector.

    This class simply delegates to an underlying injector, and is useful for subclasses of Injector that only want to modify partial behavior and delegate the rest.

    Warning: This class is part of the internal implementation for Guice lifecycle containers and should not be used directly by consumers. Instead use LifecycleContainer and GuiceLifecycleContainers.
